==English==
===Etymology===
German ''[[Quarz]]''
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''quartz'''  (''plural:'' '''[[quartzs]]''')
# {{mineralogy}} The most abundant [[mineral]] on the earth's surface.  It occurs in a variety of forms, both [[crystal]]line and [[amorphous]].  Found in every environment.

*Chemical composition: Silicon dioxide, <math>SiO_2</math>

